### **New Top-Up Flow:**

1. Customer clicks **"Top Up"** button
2. Selects amount ($10, $20, $50, $100) or enters custom amount
3. Clicks **"Pay with PayNow / Card"**
4. Redirects to **Stripe Checkout** (PayNow QR or card payment)
5. After payment â†’ Redirects back to app
6. **Webhook automatically adds credits** to customer account
7. Success message shown

